title: Living In The Faith Zone | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Living In The Faith Zone | Joel Osteen
description:
Throughout life, God presents us with opportunities that in the natural, we may not think we can handle. But if you’ll be bold and take a step of faith, God will help you accomplish things greater than you ever thought possible.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
